create spring starter project 
boot : 2.0.4
1.no dependencies added
2.spring boot application class used as test class
3.spring boot application class marked as componentScan("com.example.bean")
4.mark bean(person) as component
5.no need to mark Spring boot application class as configuration class. 
6.spring boot app provides context, through which we can ask spring container to provide dependencies.
Ex : ConfigurableApplicationContext context = SpringApplication.run(DemoApplication.class, args);
